{"tid":1205723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新香港旗？","createTime":"2019-06-11T22:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T18:46:09.000Z","uid":10207,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13eaf112ba2aafebd0b7eeaf9d12571153f44b80","tid":1205723,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16rMML.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16rMML.png&h=d7fb2e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離post睇到<br />\n<br />\n用有代表性嘅旗對士氣好重要，咪用人地國家旗或者港獅旗咁on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99706930b624b1c75c0826c29837ec9213cb0e62","tid":1205723,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:01:00.000Z","msg":"核突抽氣扇"},{"pid":"ec19c37e2aeb554e0c77d3fac55a4c4622049798","tid":1205723,"uid":34523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:02:05.000Z","msg":"中間個窿好核突"},{"pid":"77b2313a42df97f85578cc4df9da14ee96b8db10","tid":1205723,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:04:50.000Z","msg":"又唔係我設計嘅，大家可以諗個更好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1f7bdd185436a40d801267493d7e8d32375941","tid":1205723,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔好抄現有支區旗"},{"pid":"8dcd959d7f135c1b7a4e7a0dfe32c239fc9a650d","tid":1205723,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"唔用抽氣扇啦"},{"pid":"687de949ef922659d9b17ae78bb6ad51bb5762b1","tid":1205723,"uid":291957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DOPfqc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DOPfqc.png&h=c40058d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個聽到香港之歌 就忍唔L住鼻酸酸眼濕濕嘅人，因為過去三個月 香港人實在經歷了太多苦難...我哋香港人將手足的痛視為自己的痛，將手足嘅命視為自己的命，即使面對港共暴政肆意踐踏、打壓甚至攞命，香港人都冇半點退縮，因為我哋係香港人！為香港而生！甘為香港而犧牲！<br />\n<br />\n講返首歌，我每次在街上聽到都會暫停腳步，肅立，右手放在胸前，大聲唱出香港之歌。但我發現好多人都玩電話，周圍望！我相信同我哋沒有一支真正代表香港既旗有關！我哋需要一支香港旗凝聚人心，有旗就有家，有家就有國！我想像到一邊唱香港歌，一邊望住香港旗徐徐升起，又或在戰場前線，不論前中後排都向著旗方向義無反顧地勇往直前。香港旗將是香港人的勇氣，希望，見證香港人的苦難，癒合所有香港人的身和心。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我不自量地同朋友組成【香港之旗團隊】，好想集合大家的意見及設定，去創造一枝能代表香港嘅旗！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【香港之旗設計大賽】</span></span><br />\n活動會分主要兩個階段<br />\n階段一：收集設計 <br />\n大家藝術人/設計師可將設計發送到電郵：hongkongflag2019@gmail.com<br />\n / 或TG: @hongkongflag<br />\n 1. 不大於1 Gb 的JPG 檔案<br />\n 2. 連同你的創作意念 (不多於200字）<br />\n 3. 所有投稿都會以匿名發表<br />\n 4. 必須要是原創<br />\n<br />\n階段二：全民投票<br />\n到時會於合適的平台，供大家投票<br />\n(詳細資料，之後公佈）<br />\n<br />\n香港國旗，由你決定！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n想討論？可去以下TG group: <br />\n <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Ndm9DhXqd9p3ZHosNDNggQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNdm9DhXqd9p3ZHosNDNggQ&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=4184cc2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Ndm9DhXqd9p3ZHosNDNggQ</a>"},{"pid":"0adad940952c8649b75ffe1d00ea8d6ab79b892c","tid":1205723,"uid":312672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"香港大鵬金翅鳥國旗<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iV7u08agP0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiV7u08agP0U&d=NC%2FTzFAtl3V7yegmN9swvnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6d545770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iV7u08agP0U</a>"},{"pid":"72c2babe7a8794d1c316e8af80017a5d68fd4d13","tid":1205723,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T18:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1EuWwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1EuWwF.png&h=2cb7e309&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}